@startuml
!define ICONS /Users/iworldafric/dev/diagrams/plantuml-stdlib/stdlib/tupadr3
!include ICONS/font-awesome-5/brain.puml
!include ICONS/font-awesome-5/database.puml
!include ICONS/font-awesome-5/memory.puml
!include ICONS/font-awesome-5/cog.puml
!include ICONS/font-awesome-5/eye.puml
!include ICONS/common.puml

skinparam dpi 150
skinparam defaultFontName "Segoe UI"
skinparam defaultFontSize 12
skinparam ActivityBackgroundColor #1A5276
skinparam ActivityBorderColor #2980B9
skinparam ActivityFontColor #FFFFFF
skinparam ActivityFontSize 13
skinparam ActivityArrowColor #5DADE2
skinparam ActivityArrowFontColor #2C3E50
skinparam ActivityDiamondBackgroundColor #117A65
skinparam ActivityDiamondBorderColor #1ABC9C
skinparam ActivityDiamondFontColor #FFFFFF
skinparam ActivityStartColor #2ECC71
skinparam ActivityEndColor #E74C3C
skinparam shadowing true
skinparam RoundCorner 12
skinparam Padding 8

title Memory Fabric — Data Flow

start

:<$eye> **Raw Observations**
Environment signals, tool outputs,
conversation events arriving as structured JSON;

:<$brain> **Memory Formation**
Tag with timestamp, context, source ID.
Score salience (0.0–1.0) via attention model.
Compress to embedding vector (1536-dim);

:<$cog> **Topology Update**
Insert node into memory graph.
Link to related nodes (cosine similarity > 0.75).
Update tier weights: Working → Episodic → Semantic;

:<$database> **Retrieval Index**
Build BM25 + vector hybrid index.
Prune stale nodes (decay λ = 0.01/hour).
Promote high-frequency nodes to faster tier;

:<$memory> **Curated Context**
Retrieve top-k memories by query relevance.
Re-rank by recency × salience × tier weight.
Return as structured context for next LLM call;

stop
@enduml
